request.doc:
Create a new property
POST https://{appliance_hostname}/wga/kerberos/config/libdefaults
POST_DATA:
{
"name":"default_realm",
"value":"example.com"
}

Create a new sub-section
POST https://{appliance_hostname}/wga/kerberos/config/realms
POST_DATA:
{
"subsection":"Example",
}

response.doc:
Create a new property
200 ok
{"id":"default_realm"}

Create a new sub-section
200 ok
{"id":"Example"}
